org.apache.hive.spark.client.metrics

Class Metrics

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hive.spark.client.metrics.Metrics
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
public class Metrics
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Metrics tracked during the execution of a job. Depending on how the metrics object is obtained (by calling methods in the `MetricsCollection` class), metrics will refer to one or more tasks.
    See Also:
